=head1 NAME

ctfi - ctf instances helper

=head1 SYNOPSIS

  # ctfi INSTANCENAME [CTFARGS ...]

=head1 DESCRIPTION

When run as root, C<ctfi INSTANCENAME> is equivalent to 
C<ctf --config /etc/ctfi/INSTANCENAME/ctf.conf>.

When run as a non-root user, it's equivalent to
C<ctf --config ~/.ctfi/INSTANCENAME/ctf.conf>.

CTFARGS are passed on to ctf(1).

=head1 SEE ALSO

ctf(1)

=cut
